 Duncan Mighty and his Ex-Wife Nigerian singer Duncan Mighty has taken to his page to slam his wife Vivian and her family again for plotting to kill him and take over his properties. In a very lengthy post on his Instagram page, Duncan Mighty tagged his wife and his family as murderers for poisoning him so he might die and take over his properties after his death. “Wherever you run to people will still recognize you and call you a murderer”. “Vivian Nwakanma and her family you’ve not started running yet if you like run to the moon the wrath of GOD must hunt you, people, you poisoned my food and bathing water for 2years and 11months but GOD ALMIGHTY stood by me, if you people have succeeded in killing me you would have told the world I died of hard drugs but MERÇY SAID NO…..”